annot.p: S solo and coro (7), A solo and coro (7), T solo and coro (7), B solo and coro (7), clno 1 (2), clno 2 (2), vl 1 (8), vl 2 (8), vla 1 (1), vla 2 (1), vlne (8), org (8)
vlne by unidentified hand, remaining parts by Istvánffy

Istvánffy rewrote the vl parts (since they are largely colla parte in Werner's version), replaced trb 1/2 by clno 1/2, and added two solo vla to the middle section of the third movement (Convertere anima mea). Moreover, he reworked several sections.
